Installation

The miss-SNF package can be installed using devtools. Please follow these steps:

  1. Download miss-SNF package from this repository.

  2. Install devtools using:

install.packages("devtools");
  1. Load devtools package:
library("devtools");
  1. Then, you can install miss-SNF (some Bioconductor packages has to be installed apart):
BiocManager::install("RBGL")
BiocManager::install("graph")
BiocManager::install("limma")
install("./missSNF");
  1. Now miss-SNF can be used as every R package:
# Load package
library(missSNF);

# View documentation
?miss.snf()
